00:53:15,928 --> 00:53:18,137
I can't find the valve!
Wentz, help Rabbit!

455
00:53:18,264 --> 00:53:21,849
Enemy submarine close aboard.
Torpedo in the water.
Torpedo in the water!

456
00:53:21,934 --> 00:53:24,435
All right, belay that.
Wentz, stay where you are!

457
00:53:24,520 --> 00:53:26,813
Hirsch, hotfoot it
to the torpedo room !

