Okay, come on.

920
01:45:14,960 --> 01:45:17,128
That blew them right in half.

921
01:45:28,641 --> 01:45:31,643
Hell, Mr. Tyler,
if you ever need a chief. . .

922
01:45:32,520 --> 01:45:34,521
